{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Listen to the story and play the right card</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a narrative game that combines card play. With the advancement of the single-line plot, you need to carefully read the plot description of each round, find clues from it, judge and play the right card to promote the development of the story. Each round, you can adjust some of your cards, and the new plot will also bring new cards to help you deal with upcoming events.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Game features:</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Immersive narrative experience - linear plot, gradually revealed stories waiting for you to explore<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3523990/extras/screenshot05.png?t=1740406723\" /></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Logic and judgment - according to the plot prompts, choose the cards that match the situation to play<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3523990/extras/screenshot04.png?t=1740406723\" /></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Dynamic deck adjustment - you can change some of your cards in each round and get new plot cards<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3523990/extras/screenshot02.png?t=1740406723\" /></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Simple and challenging - easy to get started, but you need to think carefully about every decision<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3523990/extras/screenshot03.png?t=1740406723\" /></h2>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3523990?t=1740406723","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3523990/22ba44071e15726569a2011c6f42e6259de73657/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1740406723","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/s